<item>
            <title>[MRUNIT-54] Driver.runTest throws RuntimeException should it throw AssertionError?</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MRUNIT-54</link>
                <project id="12311292" key="MRUNIT">MRUnit</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The difference is small but in maven tests show up as erred not failed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12538873">MRUNIT-54</key>
            <summary>Driver.runTest throws RuntimeException should it throw AssertionError?</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
